00:03:35.080 --> 00:03:37.316
-Yeah.
-It's just between us.

00:03:37.349 --> 00:03:40.453
-Yeah. -What-what
was one of your favorites?

00:03:40.486 --> 00:03:42.855
Well, my favorite-- I have read
it-- it's<i> Brown Girl Dreaming</i>

00:03:42.888 --> 00:03:44.857
-by Jacqueline Woodson.
So, it's a... -Oh, nice.

